comments: Osman (CLE) and Randle (NYK) engage and disengage at the high post.
Osman (CLE) places his hand to Randle's (NYK) side as he jumps to pass and does not extend or apply force.
Payton (NYK) briefly grasps Sexton's (CLE) off-arm during the drive.
After Osman (CLE) makes contact with the ball, he makes marginal contact with Morris Sr.'s (NYK) arm as he follows through to complete the pass.
Ntilikina (NYK) establishes a legal screening position in Sexton's (CLE) path however there is a briefly delay as both players disengage from the screen.
Sexton (CLE) cleanly dislodges the ball during Morris Sr.'s (NYK) dribble.
As Garland (CLE) reaches in and turns his body, he makes contact with Payton's (NYK) side that affects his driving shot attempt.
Randle (NYK) establishes a legal position in Garland's (CLE) path and firms up when contact occurs.
Nance Jr. (CLE) legally contest Randle's (NYK) play at the basket.
Osman (CLE) legally contest Morris Sr.'s (NYK) jump shot attempt.
As Randle (NYK) moves to retrieve the rebound, he places his arm around Nance Jr.'s (CLE) upper body creating marginal contact as both players engage.
Portis (NYK) briefly grasps Love's (CLE) jersey during the rebound.
Osman (CLE) commits a take foul on Morris Sr. (NYK).
Randle (NYK) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Osman's (CLE) path.
Osman (CLE) legally contest Morris Sr.'s (NYK) jump shot attempt.
Randle (NYK) briefly places a forearm on Sexton's (CLE) side during the drive.
Portis (NYK) makes contact with Love's (CLE) left arm during his upward shooting motion affecting his ability to finish at the rim.
After Payton (NYK) secures the rebound, Nance Jr. (CLE) swipes down and makes marginal contact to his body.
Morris Sr. (NYK) makes clean contact with the ball as Sexton (CLE) moves through his upward shooting motion.
Love (CLE) makes marginal contact with Randle's (NYK) body during the driving shot.
Randle (NYK) makes "high-five" contact with Love (CLE) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Morris Sr. (NYK) briefly interlocks arms with Osman (CLE) as they disengage from the screen.
Morris Sr. (NYK) makes marginal contact with Osman (CLE) as he releases to receive the pass.
Morris Sr. (NYK) makes two hand contact to Osman (CLE) at the start of his drive affecting his SQBR.
Randle (NYK) briefly grasps Love's (CLE) jersey in the post.
Portis (NYK) legally contest Nance Jr.'s (CLE) jump shot attempt.
Nance Jr.'s (CLE) shot attempt fails to make contact with the rim prior to the shot clock expiration.
Morris Sr. (NYK) makes marginal contact with Osman (CLE) as he releases to retrieve the pass on the perimeter.
Nance Jr. (CLE) and Ntilikina (NYK) engage and disengage during the inbound play.
Ntilikina (NYK) hooks Nance Jr.'s (CLE) leg and restricts his ability to rebound.
Sexton (CLE) commits a take foul on Randle (NYK).
Osman (CLE) commits a take foul on Morris Sr. (NYK).
Nance Jr. (CLE) slightly extends his hands to Bullock's (NYK) back as he releases to retrieve the rebound. The contact is marginal.
